---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AffiliateCTA from '../../components/AffiliateCTA.astro';
import { AFFILIATE_LINKS as affiliates } from '../../config/affiliate-links';

const title = 'AI Website Builder Mistakes to Avoid (2025)';
const description = 'I tested AI website builders for 200+ hours. Here are the costly mistakes people make and how to avoid them.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold mb-4">GUIDE</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">AI Website Builder Mistakes to Avoid</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Learn from others' failures. These mistakes cost time, money, and frustration.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">The #1 Mistake</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg">
        <strong>Choosing the wrong platform then migrating later.</strong> Switching costs hours of work. Choose right the first time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Costly Mistakes (And How to Avoid Them)</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. Ignoring Vendor Lock-In</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The mistake:</strong> Building on Wix, then realizing you can't export your site. You're stuck or start over.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> Check code export BEFORE building. If you might leave, choose Framer (React export) or Dorik (HTML export).
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Reality check:</strong> Most AI builders lock you in. Assume no export unless explicitly confirmed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">2. Over-Paying for Features You Don't Need</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The mistake:</strong> Paying $23/month for Squarespace when a $3 Hostinger site would work.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> Start with the cheapest plan that works. Upgrade only when you hit actual limits.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Reality check:</strong> Most people over-buy. Start small, scale as needed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. Expecting AI to Write Perfect Copy</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The mistake:</strong> Publishing AI-generated text without editing. It sounds generic and robotic.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> Use AI as a first draft. Always add your voice, specifics, and personality.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Reality check:</strong> AI copy is a starting point, not finished work.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Not Testing Mobile</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The mistake:</strong> Building on desktop, assuming mobile works. Then realizing your site is broken on phones.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> Test mobile view continuously. 60% of traffic is mobile - it matters more than desktop.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Reality check:</strong> Most AI builders handle mobile well, but test anyway.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">5. Choosing Flash Over Substance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The mistake:</strong> Picking Framer for beautiful animations, then realizing it lacks features you need.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> Prioritize features over aesthetics. A pretty site that doesn't work is useless.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Reality check:</strong> Function first, design second.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">6. Forgetting About Scaling</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The mistake:</strong> Building a simple site on a limited platform, then hitting walls when you grow.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> Think 6 months ahead. Will you need ecommerce? Blogging? Member areas? Choose a platform that scales.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Reality check:</strong> Migrating later is painful. Plan for growth now.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">7. Skipping the Free Trial</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The mistake:</strong> Paying without testing. Then realizing you hate the editor or it doesn't do what you need.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> ALWAYS use free trials. Test everything before paying.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Reality check:</strong> Most builders offer 14-30 days. Use them.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">8. Not Setting Up Custom Domain Properly</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The mistake:</strong> Using builder-brand.com for months. Looks unprofessional and hurts SEO.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            <strong>The fix:</strong> Buy your domain immediately. Set it up before launching. It's $15/year, worth every cent.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Reality check:</strong> Your domain is your brand. Own it from day one.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">How to Choose Right (First Time)</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Step 1:</strong> Define your MUST-HAVE features (ecommerce? booking? blog?)</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Step 2:</strong> Check 3-5 builders support those features</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Step 3:</strong> Use free trials on your shortlist</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Step 4:</strong> Build a test page on each</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Step 5:</strong> Choose the one that felt easiest</p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mt-6">
        <strong>Time investment:</strong> 2-3 hours of testing saves 20+ hours of migrating later.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Quick Platform Recommendations</h2>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Content-heavy sites:</strong> 10Web + WordPress</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Design portfolios:</strong> Framer or Squarespace</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Ecommerce:</strong> 10Web + WooCommerce or Squarespace</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Simple business sites:</strong> Durable or Hostinger</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Complex/custom:</strong> Webflow</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <AffiliateCTA
        href={affiliates['10web'].affiliateUrl}
        commission={affiliates['10web'].commission}
        label="Start Free Trial (No Commitment)"
        className="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg inline-block"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Related Reviews -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-[#F5521A]"></div>Related Reviews
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/reviews/codedesign-ai" class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-200 hover:border-[#F5521A] transition-all group">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-black text-white">EXP</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] mb-1">CodeDesign.ai</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Avoid lock-in. Clean HTML/CSS export available.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/reviews/framer-ai" class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-200 hover:border-[#F5521A] transition-all group">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-black text-white">EXP</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] mb-1">Framer AI</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">React export option. Best for avoiding lock-in.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/reviews/hostinger-ai" class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-200 hover:border-[#F5521A] transition-all group">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-purple-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-xl font-black text-white">$3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] mb-1">Hostinger AI</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Avoid overpaying. Start at $2.99/mo.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/reviews/10web-ai" class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-200 hover:border-[#F5521A] transition-all group">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-black text-white">EC</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#F5521A] mb-1">10Web AI</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Scales with you. WordPress for growth.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
